casebody.data:
FOSTER, Respondent, v. HOOKER et al., Appellants. (Superior Court of New York City,

General Term.

December 23, 1895.) Action by Daniel Foster against Walter W. Hooker. Abram F. Servin, for appellants. Abeam ICling, for respondent. PER CURIAM.

The order should be affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
